@startuml REQ-0060 Device Provisioning
autonumber

entity "User Action" as User_Action

box "System" #LightBlue
  participant "Provisioning Manager" as Provisioning_Manager
  participant "WiFi Scanner" as WiFi_Scanner
  participant "Cert Manager" as Cert_Manager
  participant "Comm Manager" as Comm_Manager
end box

header
  **REQ-0060: Device Provisioning**
  //Description:// Orchestrate device provisioning: scan networks, join, and install certificates.
  //Acceptance Criteria:// Device progresses through scan/join/cert states. Provisioning completes or retries on failure.
end header


User_Action -> Provisioning_Manager: EVENT:FACTORY_RESET_COMPLETE
note right of Provisioning_Manager: PROV_STATE_INIT
Provisioning_Manager --> WiFi_Scanner: EVENT:PROV_SCAN_START\nProvision_Start() → WiFiScan_Start()
WiFi_Scanner --> Provisioning_Manager: EVENT:PROV_SCAN_COMPLETE\nWiFiScan_Start() → Provision_OnScanComplete()
alt (count > 0)
Provisioning_Manager --> WiFi_Scanner: EVENT:PROV_JOIN_REQUEST\nProvision_OnScanComplete() → WiFiScan_Join()
WiFi_Scanner --> Provisioning_Manager: EVENT:PROV_JOIN_RESULT\nWiFiScan_Join() → Provision_OnJoinResult()
else
Provisioning_Manager --> Provisioning_Manager: EVENT:PROV_FAILED
end alt
note right of Provisioning_Manager: PROV_RETRY_CHECK
alt (result->success)
Provisioning_Manager --> Cert_Manager: EVENT:PROV_CERT_REQUEST\nProvision_OnJoinResult() → Cert_Provision()
Cert_Manager --> Provisioning_Manager: EVENT:PROV_CERT_INSTALLED\nCert_Provision() → Provision_OnCertInstalled()
note right of Provisioning_Manager: PROV_STATE_READY
Provisioning_Manager -> Comm_Manager: Comm_SendStatus()
Provisioning_Manager --> Provisioning_Manager: EVENT:PROV_COMPLETE
else
alt (retry_count < MAX_RETRIES)
Provisioning_Manager --> WiFi_Scanner: EVENT:PROV_SCAN_START\nProvision_OnJoinResult() → WiFiScan_Start()
end alt
end alt

@enduml